# UI/UX Revamp Packet Standards

When working on UI/UX, interaction, or motion elements in Flagship Foundry, you must adhere to the design decisions defined in the UI/UX Revamp Packet.

## Reference Packet Directory
`.foundry/staging/flagship-foundry-uiux-revamp`

## Key Rules
- **ADR-001**: Select Cockpit Shell as Canonical Operator Surface
- **ADR-002**: Separate View Registry from Runtime State
- **ADR-003**: Adopt Operator Drilldown Chain 
- **ADR-004**: Adopt Motion Toggle and Accessibility Baseline

Review the architecture guidelines and ADRs in `.foundry/staging/flagship-foundry-uiux-revamp` before proposing or making changes.
